column5: Just returned from the annual fly in trip with the Fishquest crew and had another awesome year. I'm posting a link here to my full report as I can't figure out how to post pics on here. http://www.canadafishingguide.net/fo...abi-lake-2014/ If anyone ever has any questions feel free to pm me Thanks for reading it Mike DeGrace
Great report Mike, sounds like you guys had a good time. Thanks for sharing
Thanks Phil, always a good time and enjoy trip #2 when you it comes around. Mike
